Notes: Wayne State ranked sixth in USA Today/ESPN Top 25 Coaches Poll
Wayne State wins 30th straight game at home. Ashley Arlen has third double-
double of the season with 27 points and 11 rebounds...Clare Duwelius ties
career high with six three pointers.
Game.Officials: Amy Hupke,  Darin Berg,  Seth Hansen
